raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"sorority_house\")
Jessica: Good morning future frat members
if Story.black_heart > 0:
	set Story.black_heart = 1
if Story.yellow_heart > 0:
	set Story.yellow_heart = 1
Jessica: I'd like to congratulate you all on the record for making it
Jessica: img: jessica/2
Jessica: Here's a little congratulation picture for you
Jason: Whoa
- Hot
	Player: Hot
	Jessica: 😉
	Jessica: Too bad you're just cubs 💜
- [...]
Jessica: First let's get the weekly grant out of the way
- [Claim] [#dollar] [#dollar] [if PhoneUnlocks.is_claimed(\"Frat1\") == false]
	set PhoneUnlocks.claim = \"Frat1\"
	set PhoneUnlocks.dollars += 1
- [Already Claimed] [if PhoneUnlocks.is_claimed(\"Frat1\") == true]
Jason: Whoa thanks, this is awesome
Alex: That's it?
Jessica: Now now, the girls worked really hard to keep club income high
Jessica: Isn't that right girls?
Erika: Oh yes, such hard work... 😉
Nina: Pfft
Erika: Your back couldn't handle it babe?
Erika: img: erika/11
Nina: Not in the mood for you today
Erika: Yes you are, you love me 🥰
Jessica: I have an idea
Jessica: Since they Nina and Erika have been working so hard
Jessica: Why don't you three boys call out who you'd like to take out on a date?
Jessica: All expenses paid for, let's give our girls a little break
Erika: That's so sweet Jess
Nina: What!?
- Erika [#yellowheart] [if Story.yellow_heart >= 1]
	set Story.yellow_heart += 1
	set Story.flag = \"Erika1\"
	Player: Erika
	Erika: Oh my... that was so quick 😳💛
	Erika: You'd take someone like me on a date?
	Player: Yeah, why not?
	Erika: My heart skipped a beat 🥰
	Erika: I'd love to go on a date with you
	Erika: img: erika/12
	Nina: Oh brother.. why are you acting like a princess you hoe
	Alex: I'll take the Nina chic then
	Jason: Awh man, I was too hesitant and couldn't decide lol
- Nina [#blackheart] [if Story.black_heart >= 1]
	set Story.black_heart += 1
	set Story.flag = \"Nina1\"
	Player: Nina
	Nina: What do you want?
	Nina: Wait wtf.. seriously!?
	Nina: Hell no, I'm not
	Jessica: Now now Nina, rules are rules
	Nina: Tsk, fuck this
	Nina: You fuckin perv 🤬
	Nina: img: nina/17
	Player: 😌
	if Story.has_flag(\"NinasPanties\"):
		Erika: Congratulations Nina 🥰 My favorite ship is sailing
		Erika: Please treat her well
		Nina: Fuck you too
	Alex: I guess I'll take the Erika chic then
	Erika: Hey hot stuff 🥰
	Jason: Awh man, I was too hesitant and couldn't decide lol
- [...]
	set Story.flag = \"FratNoDate1\"
	Alex: I'll take the Nina chic then
	Jason: Sure, I'll go with Erika woo
	Erika: Can't wait 🥰
Jessica: The last member will have to sit this week out unfortunately
Nina: Tch, we're not up for grabs
Nina: Besides, why didn't you include Val?
Jessica: Val's currently occupied with a little task I set up for her tonight
Jessica: That new girl needs a little exposure
Nina: Heh, I see
if Story.has_flag(\"NinasPanties\"):
	Nina: I wouldn't mind volunteering for that
	Jessica: Noted
Erika: 👀
Jessica: Anyway, you have until next week to set something up in your pairs
Jessica: The girls will report back to me and tell me how it went
Jessica: Oh, and Frat cubs aren't allowed to screw until they're fully fledged
Erika: I hate that rule 😣
Jessica: Rules are rules
Jessica: See you next week
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
